{"tid":579702,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"變態修女舔耶穌的包皮產生性高潮","createTime":"2018-03-03T21:35:39.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-04T01:02:10.000Z","uid":160807,"like":7,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"32a84d2c414be057a7a75747e9e61823beb3e579","tid":579702,"uid":160807,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-03T21:35:39.000Z","msg":"奧地利修女Agnes Blannbekin，1260年加入維也納法蘭西斯第三教團後，她拒絕再吃肉，聲稱耶穌的內體能滿足她，這話不是開玩笑的。 <br />\n<br />\n她聲稱嘗聖體並喝從耶穌被刺傷肋部流下的令人興奮的聖靈水，這時耶穌會讓她產生性高潮，她也有沉溺於聖包皮的癖好，她能感受耶穌的包皮在她的嘴裡 <br />\n<br />\n她的幻覺由一位聖方濟各會的修士紀錄下來:「她感受到耶穌在十字架受苦而哭泣，開始想到當地的耶穌的聖包皮」「看呀，不久她感到從吞嚥的舌頭裡嘗 到像雞蛋膜大小包皮的甜味」「她吞嚥下後又感到另一片更甜的小包皮，如此再三，得樂百多次，她想用指頭去摸」「當她想如此做時，有一片包皮進入她的喉內， 然後她被告知耶穌的聖包皮會與耶穌復活日時一同復活，品嚐如此美味小包皮後，她感到全身上下是如此的甜密」<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://theholyprepuce.tumblr.com/post/7382086542/the-nun-who-ate-the-holy-foreskin-of-jesus\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ftheholyprepuce.tumblr.com%2Fpost%2F7382086542%2Fthe-nun-who-ate-the-holy-foreskin-of-jesus&d=sOENwHjyvEI3yH8occPVRkbWhtBCnEJYRTWbVbFBOac%3D&h=503ebe32\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://theholyprepuce.tumblr.com/post/7382086542/the-nun-who-ate-the-holy-foreskin-of-jesus</a><br />\n(註:原始網站文章有附圖片)"},{"pid":"8e5524f77ba8c7456371b5473d213d3b65b6e2b0","tid":579702,"uid":4575,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-03T21:58:48.000Z","msg":"聖精呢"},{"pid":"f7f9dd654739e7cbe7a390899eb84ce581850036","tid":579702,"uid":55249,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-03T22:02:07.000Z","msg":"神交<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"01bd485d2543ad84bfc704574d175136f36c4dd3","tid":579702,"uid":160807,"like":22,"dislike":2,"score":20,"citedBy":7,"replyTime":"2018-03-03T22:16:32.000Z","msg":"有冇巴打知呢個係咩野來<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/as